ygData.messageBody:
You're missing a lot by not going to Broken Skull. I spend a lot of
time in Dulak and now Nadox. The models are great and the loot is
good. Most of the charms have a component in Dulak or Gunthak. You
gotta go.

Yeah, touch the doors on the boat and you're in Gunthak. Run across
the water to the beach. From there are tunnels to Dulak or Nadox.
Anyone from 35 to 65 can something to do.
